Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:38.90,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}想要时刻在你身边　时刻守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:43.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}除此之外别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:44.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.72,0:01:49.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}如果说　这都是你的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:50.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Trust you
