Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:55.66,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}ooh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:59.36,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那我也甘愿背叛一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:10.54,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我和你　在一起的时光虽不是永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:16.84,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}即使有一天我消失不见
